<div class="user-guide-page container">
  <h1><%= page.title %></h1>
  <p class="lead"><%= page.description %></p>

  <div class="guide-screenshot mb-4">
    <img src="<%= page.screenshotUrl %>" alt="<%= page.title %> screenshot" class="img-fluid border" />
  </div>

  <h2>Manage your club sponsors</h2>
  <p>This section allows you to add, remove, and manage sponsors linked to your club profile.</p>

  <h3>Adding a sponsor</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Click <em>Add Sponsor</em>.</li>
    <li>Enter sponsor name, description, website, and upload a logo if available.</li>
    <li>Choose whether the sponsor is publicly visible on the site.</li>
    <li>Save to attach the sponsor to your club.</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>Editing sponsors</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Click <em>Edit</em> next to a sponsor to change details or upload a new logo.</li>
    <li>Toggle the visibility flag to hide or show the sponsor publicly.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="mt-3"><a href="<%= page.url %>">Open the Manage Sponsors page</a></p>
  <p><a href="/user-guide">Back to guide index</a></p>
</div>
